        <h1>Offline Music Library</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Source and Acquisition</h2>
            <p>This collection of music primarily originates from my <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/313qihdhnjtslad6fjhcq562alo4?si=2t2hTYn1TImVErUwXgu1eg" class="source-link">Spotify</a> & <a href="https://youtube.com/@steveharrisantony?si=exPvfXbzIbn-UeDC" class="source-link">YouTube</a> playlists. These tracks were conveniently downloaded for offline enjoyment using a third-party application called <a href="https://soundbound.app/" class="source-link"><span class="highlight">SoundBound</span></a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Audio Quality</h2>
            <p>The majority of the songs in this library boast excellent audio fidelity, encoded as high-quality <span class="highlight">MP3 files at 320kbps</span>. A smaller portion of the collection is also included at a still respectable <span class="highlight">128kbps</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Rich Metadata and Album Art</h2>
            <p>Each and every track within this collection is enriched with <span class="highlight">comprehensive metadata</span>, ensuring proper organization and identification. Furthermore, all songs feature <span class="highlight">embedded album art</span>, providing a visually appealing experience as you browse your music.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Time-Synchronized Lyrics</h2>
            <p>A significant number of tracks in this library come equipped with <span class="highlight">time-synchronized lyrics</span>, allowing you to follow along with your favorite songs. It's worth noting that most of these lyrics are predominantly in the <span class="highlight">same language as the corresponding song</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section recommendation">
            <h2>Optimal Listening Experience</h2>
            <p>For the best experience viewing the embedded time-synchronized lyrics, it is highly recommended to use music players such as <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=in.krosbits.musicolet" class="source-link"><span class="highlight">Musicolet</span></a>. These players are specifically designed to seamlessly display this embedded lyrical information.</p>
        </div>
